<h1>What is Node.js </h1>
<li>
	Node is service side javascript framework 
	It is event driven and single thread
	It is build with JavaScript V8 Google javascript engine
	Support asynchronous and none blocking code by default
	Supports modular javascript
	it is written in C, C++ and some APIs are in javascript
When to use Node
	Real-time applications
	I/O bound applications
	Data Streaming applications
When not to use
	CPU intensive operations
	
